    <briefdescription>
<para>Wi-Fi credentials entry header. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><simplesect kind="note"><para>Every settings entry starts with this header. Depending on the <computeroutput>type</computeroutput> field, the header can be casted to a larger type. In addition to SSID (usually a string) and BSSID (a MAC address), a <computeroutput>flags</computeroutput> field can be used to control some detail settings. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
